tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE data_preprocessing (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    raw_data VARCHAR(255),
    cleaned_data VARCHAR(255),
    preprocessing_steps TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE preprocess_data (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    data_column1 VARCHAR,
    data_column2 VARCHAR,
    cleaned_data_column1 VARCHAR,
    cleaned_data_column2 VARCHAR
);

CREATE TABLE machine_learning_algorithm (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    preprocessing_id INT,
    model_name VARCHAR,
    training_data_column1 VARCHAR,
    training_data_column2 VARCHAR
);
